title: The Benched Bachelorette Episode 1: Saying Goodbye

description:
Rachel Bonnetta starts her journey towards newfound fandom with a brand new series: The Benched Bachelorette. 32 teams vie for the affections of one free agent fan. Which team will she choose? On the premiere episode, one team is sent home...
